# SecureApp Cloud API

Containerized ASP.NET Core REST API deployed to Azure.

## Live API

Swagger UI  
https://secureapp-dev-usman.azurewebsites.net/swagger

## Features

- Product REST API
- CRUD operations
- Docker containerization
- Azure Container Registry
- Azure App Service deployment
- Swagger documentation

## Tech Stack

- ASP.NET Core 8
- Docker
- Azure App Service
- Azure Container Registry
- Entity Framework Core
- SQL Server

## API Endpoints

GET /api/products  
POST /api/products  
GET /api/products/{id}  
PUT /api/products/{id}  
DELETE /api/products/{id}

## Architecture

Client → REST API → Database  
Containerized with Docker → deployed to Azure App Service.

